    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mechjestic - 演示版让你一窥游戏将提供的众多可能性。你会采用什么策略来击败邪恶的无时之机？在地表世界中战斗，装备你获得的奖励卡牌，勇往直前，直面名为“Jawlock”的最终威胁！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167300/extras/bdc1e76dbdb93d2aadb4733cc3bcc04c.poster.avif?t=1769796220\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167300/extras/bdc1e76dbdb93d2aadb4733cc3bcc04c.webm?t=1769796220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167300/extras/bdc1e76dbdb93d2aadb4733cc3bcc04c.mp4?t=1769796220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >快进机甲吧，小蝌蚪</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过收集和构建你的装备卡组，你可以打出它们来改变你的机甲，并获得战斗属性。来自同一套装的五个部位全部装备时还能获得特殊加成！机甲的核心——引擎，也可以更换。不同的引擎有不同的加成，比如提供更多燃料或允许你抽更多卡牌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167300/extras/5b0432207424a342495f94ca9665133c.avif?t=1769796220\" width=600 height=258 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >幸运眷顾勇敢者……也眷顾有策略的人</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗中抽到了一张特别没用的卡？通过补给系统，你有机会扭转局势。打出卡牌或升级引擎都需要消耗燃料。如果你拿到了一手不满意的牌，这个灵活的系统允许你将卡牌回收为燃料和机会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167300/extras/54ed4c1da0f731c84b8e1977e19f4515.poster.avif?t=1769796220\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167300/extras/54ed4c1da0f731c84b8e1977e19f4515.webm?t=1769796220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167300/extras/54ed4c1da0f731c84b8e1977e19f4515.mp4?t=1769796220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无尽之池</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被雾气笼罩，每一关都要求玩家穿越谜题、宝藏和敌人。所有移动都需要消耗移动点和重置点。缺少任一都会让你更接近失败并需要重来。每通过10关，还会有更大的威胁——Boss来袭。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167300/extras/fc5f1ef97a40aa9f3fa83d5f444e7714.poster.avif?t=1769796220\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167300/extras/fc5f1ef97a40aa9f3fa83d5f444e7714.webm?t=1769796220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167300/extras/fc5f1ef97a40aa9f3fa83d5f444e7714.mp4?t=1769796220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mechjestic 正在开发中，感谢支持和资金来自:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167300/extras/7d219b3295e5381d30d375ba81b59c15.avif?t=1769796220\" width=600 height=258 /></span></p>",
